title: Yu-Gi-Oh! Power of Chaos (Complete Classic Edition Repack)
description:
Yu-Gi-Oh! Power of Chaos Classic Games (RePack)

Installation : First extract

Yugi The Destiny : Run .exe browse for instalation folder and install

Joey The Passion : Run setup for install

Kaiba The Revenge : Just extract the .7z in any random folder

Games do not auto-create shortcuts so in any case go to instalation directory and play/create shortcut from there

Seed and enjoy this release!
